@startuml
autonumber

actor "ATCC Operator" as ATCC
participant "AirportController" as Ctrl
participant "AirportRepository" as Repo
database "Base de Dados" as DB

ATCC -> Ctrl : GET /api/airports/grouped?by=country
activate Ctrl

note right of Ctrl: CQRS: Sem Use Case.\nO Controller fala com o Repository.
Ctrl -> Repo : findAll()
activate Repo

Repo -> DB : SELECT * FROM airport
activate DB
DB --> Repo : List<Airport>
deactivate DB

Repo --> Ctrl : List<Airport> airports
deactivate Repo

note right of Ctrl: O Controller agrupa a lista em memória\nusando Java Streams (Collectors.groupingBy)\nou devolve um DTO específico.
Ctrl -> Ctrl : groupAirportsByCountry(airports)

Ctrl --> ATCC : 200 OK (Map<String, List<AirportDto>>)
deactivate Ctrl
@enduml